    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Европейска агенция по производителността"@bg, "Europos produktyvumo agentūra"@lt, "Evropská agentura pro produktivitu"@cs, "Agência Europeia de Produtividade"@pt, "Európska agentúra pre produktivitu"@sk, "European Productivity Agency"@en, "Europska agencija za proizvodnost"@hr, "Euroopan tuottavuusvirasto"@fi, "Agenzia europea della produttività"@it, "Det Europæiske Produktivitetsbureau"@da, "Agencia Europea de Productividad"@es, "Európai Termelékenységi Ügynökség"@hu, "Agence européenne de productivité"@fr, "Eiropas Ražīguma aģentūra"@lv, "Evropska agencija za produktivnost"@sl, "Ευρωπαϊκός Οργανισμός Παραγωγικότητας"@el, "Euroopa Tootlikkusagentuur"@et, "Agenția Europeană de Productivitate"@ro, "Aġenzija Ewropea tal-Produttività"@mt, "Europejska Agencja ds. Produktywności"@pl, "Europees Productiviteitsagentschap"@nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The EPA had two main functions: 1) to be a clearing house, to provide the national productivity bodies and other institutions with information and other services, 2) to be a centre for study and discussion designed to guide European efforts towards a continuing improvement in productivity and in the study of the social and economic consequences of technological development. The EPA was defined as a quasi-independent body within the OEEC."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "EPA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001302"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "EPA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "ΕΟΠ"@el, "EAP"@nl, "EPA OECD"@hr, "EPA"@lt, "EPA"@lv, "EPA"@en, "EPA"@sk, "AEP"@it, "AEP"@pt, "AEP"@sl, "AEP"@fr, "AEP"@es;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EPA_1952_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "EPA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "EPA";
