    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Οργανισμός της Ευρωπαϊκής Ένωσης για τα Ναρκωτικά"@el, "Agence de l’Union européenne sur les drogues"@fr, "Agentura Evropské unie pro drog"@cs, "European Union Drugs Agency"@en, "Agencija Europske unije za droge"@hr, "L-Aġenzija tal-Unjoni Ewropea dwar id-Drogi"@mt, "Gníomhaireacht Drugaí an Aontais Eorpaigh"@ga, "Agenția Uniunii Europene privind Drogurile"@ro, "Agencija Evropske unije za droge"@sl, "Drugsagentschap van de Europese Unie"@nl, "Az Európai Unió Kábítószer-ügynöksége"@hu, "Euroopa Liidu Uimastiamet"@et, "Agência da União Europeia sobre Drogas"@pt, "Agentúra Európskej únie pre drogy"@sk, "Europos Sąjungos narkotikų agentūra"@lt, "Agenzia dell’Unione europea sulle droghe"@it, "Drogenagentur der Europäischen Union"@de, "Agencia de la Unión Europea sobre Drogas"@es, "Euroopan unionin huumevirasto"@fi, "Europeiska unionens narkotikamyndighet"@sv, "Eiropas Savienības Narkotiku aģentūra"@lv, "Агенция на Европейския съюз по наркотиците"@bg, "Agencja Unii Europejskiej ds. Narkotyków"@pl, "Den Europæiske Unions Narkotikaagentur"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Union Drugs Agency (EUDA) is the central authority on illicit drugs in the European Union. Formerly known as the EMCDDA, the Lisbon-based agency contributes to EU preparedness on drugs through actions that anticipate and alert on dangers, whilst responding to emerging issues and learning from best practice in the field to assess the effectiveness of interventions."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "TD"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "9408"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "10.2810"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "COB0001820"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "EUDA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "EUDA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "EUDA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Euda"@sv, "EUDA"@bg, "EUDA"@da, "EUDA"@ro, "EUDA"@fr, "EUDA"@es, "EUDA"@hr, "EUDA"@cs, "EUDA"@ga, "EUDA"@pt, "EUDA"@lv, "EUDA"@it, "EUDA"@el, "EUDA"@et, "EUDA"@en, "EUDA"@hu, "EUDA"@sk, "EUDA"@fi, "EUDA"@lt, "EUDA"@de, "EUDA"@mt, "EUDA"@pl, "EUDA"@sl, "EUDA"@nl;
